              "WarningsOrContraIndicationDescription": [
                {
                  "LanguageCode": "en",
                  "Value": "In case of pregnancy, circulatory problems, osteoarthritis, rheumatism or diabetes,  consult a doctor before use. Do not use in case of hypersensitivity or insensitivity to heat or cold. Everyone experiences warmth or cold differently, therefore always follow your personal feelings. Do not use in combination with pain-relieving cream and/or ointment. Never apply the compress directly to the skin. Heat only in a microwave oven. Settings may vary per microwave. Do not use if the compress is leaking. After leakage, avoid contact with skin, eyes or mouth. In case of contact, rinse immediately with water. Use in children only under adult supervision. Report serious incidents to manufacturer and competent authority. Store in original container. It contains important information."
